    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092240/extras/b18b9f958963b94cb8c5344e01f5fa6d.avif?t=1771733111\" width=1560 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete in galactic rivalry in this multiplayer sport-FPS hybrid. Work with your team to run, pass, and shoot a planet-killer bomb into the opposing team’s rift. Fight for every inch, coordinate tactics, and expend an arsenal of class-based loadouts to dominate in the arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092240/extras/f1acfa9436e37217c93380faf2da4db7.poster.avif?t=1771733111\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092240/extras/f1acfa9436e37217c93380faf2da4db7.webm?t=1771733111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092240/extras/f1acfa9436e37217c93380faf2da4db7.mp4?t=1771733111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092240/extras/51d2f7463e208156f07746faaf4d8b5f.avif?t=1771733111\" width=1560 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between one of three classes to play, each fulfilling a unique role within the team. Each class has a different primary gun, secondary gun, power weapon, equipment ability, grenade, and melee attack. Use your arsenal, equipment, and movement to execute skillful strategies, and  coordinate your abilities with your team to great effect. With katanas, grapple hooks, and gravity bombs - There’s no shortage of surprises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092240/extras/ced5eaa1aebdb9efe4a1f3da8e9921f0.avif?t=1771733111\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092240/extras/4133433f27c9b45cb34a9ad1b0368f99.avif?t=1771733111\" width=1560 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The competitive maps and modes are tightly designed for dynamic gameplay that highlight skill expression. Learn and perfect the art of controlling a physics-based bomb (ball) with precision, while balancing fast paced shooter action. Utilize fast reflexes and quick thinking in a variety of playstyles to win! There are periodically-hosted dedicated servers for quickplay matchmaking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092240/extras/0ac8516409a5f79628bfdf8ffd936c89.avif?t=1771733111\" width=1560 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The casual maps and modes are simply designed for good fun, providing interesting obstacles to overcome and enable players to explore the game's mechanics in novel environments. All classes and play styles will get a kick out of it, even if you aren't playing optimally. Here, we keep things fresh, change up the rules, and have some laughs.</p>",
